      "title_at_amendment": "Fire extinguishing system materials.",
      "text": "For all airplanes with engine(s) embedded in the fuselage or in pylons on the aft fuselage the following applies: (a) No material in any fire extinguishing system may react chemically with any extinguishing agent so as to create a hazard.\n(b) Each system component in an engine compartment must be fireproof. -",
